x index : par thème et par auteur. Le but ultime est de promouvoir la reconnaissance de la qualité significative, aussi bien que la quantité impressionnante, du travail accompli pendant ces années, de faciliter l’accès à ces études et de promouvoir l’utilisation de ces contributions diverses à la connaissance afin de stimuler la recherche et l’intervention présentes et futures. _____________________________________________________ The present book constitutes an overview of research done in French and in English during the last twenty-five years in the general area of work, in all its forms and in all its implications. The result is a striking 3,627 titles produced from the mid-1990’s to the end of 2017. The book also contains two indexes : by theme and by author. The purpose of all this is, of course, to promote recognition of the remarkable quality, and noteworthy quantity, of work accomplished during these years, to facilitate access to this body of material, and to promote the use these various contributions to our knowledge in order to stimulate present, as well as future, research and action.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aIndustrial relationsvBibliography. 0aLaborxResearchvBibliography. 0aWorkxResearchvBibliography. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Business Communication / General.2bisacsh1 aGiasson, Guylaine, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311127221408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021z978311127464540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763754642423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763754642/original  a978-3-11-127221-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-127464-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021b2021  